cy of persons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Member Conduct<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n10.1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;You may not use the AntsNest Services for any purpose that is unlawful or prohibited by the Terms of Use and/or any applicable additional terms, including the Rules, found. Your access to the AntsNest Services may be terminated immediately, in our sole discretion, with or without notice, if you fail to comply with any provision of the Terms of Use and/or additional terms, including the Rules, or for any other reason, or no reason. You expressly agree not to:<br />\r\n10.1.1.Act as an agent, affiliate or representative of the AntsNest Services and utilize the AntsNest Services or Professionals Content or Site Content for any commercial purpose other than for which the AntsNest Services is intended without our express written permission,<br />\r\n10.1.2.Access, monitor or copy any content or information of the AntsNest Services using any robot, spider, scraper or other automated means or any manual process for any purpose without our express written permission,<br />\r\n10.1.3.Take any action that imposes, or may impose, in our discretion, an unreasonable or disproportionate burden on our infrastructure, or<br />\r\n10.1.4.&ldquo;Frame,&rdquo; &ldquo;mirror&rdquo; or otherwise incorporate any part of the AntsNest Services into any other website without our prior written permission.<br />\r\n10.2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;You agree not to use the AntsNest Services for any commercial use, without the prior written authorization of AntsNest. Prohibited commercial uses include any of the following actions taken without our express approval:<br />\r\n10.2.1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Sale of access to the AntsNest Services on another website,<br />\r\n10.2.2.Use of the AntsNest Services for the primary purpose of gaining advertising or subscription revenue,<br />\r\n10.2.3.Sale of advertising on the AntsNest Services or any third- party website, targeted specific Professiona